        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Pace as an 18-time starter in the Rolex 24 and the overall winner back in 1996 when along with Scott Sharp and Wayne Taylor he piloted an Oldsmobile to take the checkered flag. During his Rolex 24 at Dayton debut in 1990, Pace was a GTU class winner. He was also victorious at the Twelve Hours of ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "Sebring",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
